{"tid":720852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉小麗以團體成員身分加入工黨","createTime":"2018-06-28T08:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T09:57:46.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed90a560495d68bcd51575db5e7d5b7582067fb","tid":720852,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"立法會九龍西補選今年十一月舉行，民主派有共識由原議員劉小麗出戰，惟她推薦由工黨李卓人作為「Plan B」的做法，惹來質疑。工黨昨證實本周一執委會已投票表決，一致通過批准劉小麗用「小麗民主教室」身分，以團體成員形式加入，但以工黨身分參選則需要再經執委會通過。劉小麗回應查詢時拒絕評論，只稱日內會作出交代。<br />\n<br />\n曾被取消議員資格的劉小麗，面臨被「二度DQ」危機，早前向民主派推薦由工黨李卓人作為「Plan B」，大部分參與協調的民主派組織均同意安排，惟民協堅持反對欽點，認為替補人選必須透過初選進行。工黨主席郭永健證實，本周一執委會一致通過讓「小麗民主教室」，以團體成員身分加入工黨，目前程序只欠繳交相關費用，又稱日後雙方會更緊密合作。郭永健指，劉小麗加入工黨與補選關係不大，稱團體成員機制為連結更多公民團體，屬下成員不等於自動加入成為黨員，若劉小麗以工黨身分參選，亦需再經執委會通過。<br />\n<br />\n提高李卓人替補正當性<br />\n<br />\n外界普遍認為劉小麗加入工黨的目的，是提高由李卓人作替補的正當性，有反對欽點的民協中人質疑，劉與工黨倘若「志氣相投」，何不一早加入，「動作明顯是為了補選」，但按民主動力的機制字眼而言，「她用工黨作後備，是無可厚非，很難說甚麼」，而劉小麗加入工黨也令民協有下台階。<br />\n<br />\n盛傳有意參選的民協馮檢基批評，有關做法是「走法律罅」，「在制度捐窿捐罅好難睇」，認為當初被「DQ」的是「小麗民主教室」的劉小麗，再參選的人應屬同一組織，「否則全港七百萬人任你揀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1251990/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1251990%2F&d=ru7BXlD9JOrC8aP0jmFt%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c807657c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1251990%2F&h=0498261d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1251990/</a>"},{"pid":"34914d802fa81f29e72a932d4e7887a9a4061e15","tid":720852,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"工黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c434a39ab1de9c129f6a48754fdffd451a9b9c6f","tid":720852,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"haha.....<br />\n<br />\n由始至終都係泛民個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748b7ea666940b7ecd91e003c58c5c1df0ee6fb3","tid":720852,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c434a39ab1de9c129f6a48754fdffd451a9b9c6f","tid":720852,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"haha.....<br />\n<br />\n由始至終都係泛民個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"幾時唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ac71de517f262cd3f3492e592cedcd11646432","tid":720852,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"呢次九萬六一定冇走雞喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3dae8eace99773e48c0e1a4654f36f228d339a","tid":720852,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:30:38.000Z","msg":"工黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f543758404447fec358aa18bd2381ba63e30a439","tid":720852,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"c8bf277a459d7e59918f2d8bfe032032ab6c6c50","tid":720852,"uid":192004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6c95690e9c1d3e5065ce05ea2b18a89421c14e2","tid":720852,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"支持馮檢基加入工黨"},{"pid":"3b13ef8d252ec29bb1ca940e48d6c4b39ca27492","tid":720852,"uid":95497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,